### SECTION 9: PARTIAL UPDATE TESTS (NO DATA LOSS)
### ===================================

### 9.1 Create a user first
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Update",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "email": "update.test@techhive.com",
  "jobTitle": "Original Title",
  "department": "Original Department",
  "hireDate": "2023-01-01",
  "isActive": true
}

### 9.2 Update only firstName (should preserve other fields)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "UpdatedName",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "",
  "jobTitle": "",
  "department": "",
  "hireDate": "0001-01-01",
  "isActive": true
}

### 9.3 Verify fields were preserved
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/4

