### SECTION 11: VALID OPERATIONS
### ===================================

### 11.1 Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### 11.2 Get specific user by ID (1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1

### 11.3 Get users by department
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/department/Engineering

### 11.4 Update user with valid data
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@techhive.com",
  "jobTitle": "Senior Software Engineer",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "hireDate": "2022-01-15",
  "isActive": true
}

### 11.5 Delete a user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/5

