### SECTION 12: ADVANCED FILTERING
### ===================================

### 12.1 Get all Engineering users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/department/Engineering

### 12.2 Get all HR users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/department/Human%20Resources

### 12.3 Get all IT users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/department/IT

