### SECTION 13: ERROR SCENARIOS (SHOULD FAIL GRACEFULLY)
### ===================================

### 13.1 Create user with empty body
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### 13.2 Create with only firstName
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Incomplete"
}

### 13.3 Delete non-existent user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/99999

### 13.4 Get non-existent user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/99999

### 13.5 Get with empty department filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/department/
